Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:44.34,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.18,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.46,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.50,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.45,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:12.14,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:21.73,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:30.92,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:40.18,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:47.50,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.95,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:44.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:12.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:21.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:30.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:40.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:47.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:03.20,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:08.23,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:12.58,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.54,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:22.22,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:26.99,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:32.05,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.70,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:44.27,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:49.09,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:54.75,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.21,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.14,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:08.98,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.08,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:19.26,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.79,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}太阳也终会升起吧
